" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"316c3fce279572a3ceb919a2fe6627b79829ee44","tid":1567293,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d831eb2aa2727b244564e7e72cacf1ff3eccb3b","tid":1567293,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67e9dfdb9ce5749d28472ef49fba0d6a4c7a1229","tid":1567293,"uid":14103,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:27:29.000Z","msg":"之前董建華賴通識令學生睇到問題 已經有人笑佢 反問不如賴體育堂令到學生體能咁好<br />\n<br />\n估唔到真係有藍絲咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"藍屍乜屎都賴"},{"pid":"88095aa19e98b3c76ed319b60e231cf97dca2b37","tid":1567293,"uid":12007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:41:43.000Z","msg":"咁捉哂田徑班人啦"},{"pid":"5ca94a24bc8a40bcd6cd37eb639206e55c9581ea","tid":1567293,"uid":101963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"對付藍絲應該借力打力，順水推舟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568616</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8b774f02147372e170e4820375e9d590add93d09","tid":1567293,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29af96da8fd6dbc9571bec3b48a8b507b5f05c94","tid":1567293,"uid":20194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b893976c20898eb6536443f0449f237efd5fb5c3","tid":15672